<section>
  <h2>Accessibility</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>The component renders a native <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> &mdash; fully keyboard accessible.</li>
    <li>The raw-mode toggle uses a native <code>&lt;input type="checkbox"&gt;</code> inside a <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>.</li>
    <li>The component sets <code>role="group"</code> on itself when both button and toggle are present.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

